Quick start
===========

    % ryu-manager --verbose ryu/dpi/ipv6sw.py

REST API
========

    # GET
    % curl http://SDNHOST:8080/stats/switches
    % curl http://SDNHOST:8080/stats/desc/<dpid>
    % curl http://SDNHOST:8080/stats/flow/<dpid>
    % curl http://SDNHOST:8080/stats/port/<dpid>
    % curl ... | python -mjson.tool

    # PUT
    % curl http://SDNHOST:8080/dpi/flow -X PUT -d "{'dpi':'on'}"

    # DELETE
    % curl http://SDNHOST:8080/stats/flowentry/clear/<dpid> -X DELETE

OVS commands
============

    # ovs-vsctl show
    # ovs-vsctl list bridge
    # ovs-vsctl list controller
    # ovs-vsctl list port

    # ovs-dpctl show

    # ovs-ofctl show <br>
    # ovs-ofctl dump-flows <br>
    # ovs-ofctl dump-ports <br>
    # ovs-ofctl dump-ports-desc <br>

    # ovs-ofctl snoop <br>
    # ovs-appctl dpif/dump-flows <br>

    # ovsdb-tool show-log
